title: Migrants bused to DC as part of Texas Gov. Abbott's protest against Biden - CNN
content:

description: A group of migrants bused from Texas arrived in Washington, DC, on Wednesday morning, after Texas Gov. Greg Abbott said he would send willing migrants to the capital in a rebuke of President Joe Biden's border policies.
